<h1><img title="About Internode" alt="About Internode" src="/media/images/titles/general/header/head-aboutinternode.jpg" height="114" width="590"></h1>
<!-- #EndEditable -->
<!-- #BeginEditable "string_Title" -->
<!-- #EndEditable -->


	<!-- #BeginEditable "stringlong_ByLine" -->
<div class="ByLine">
	<div class="ByLineSpacing"></div>
	<div>
		Internode is a subsidiary of iiNet Limited. We provide high quality, stress-free broadband Internet and phone services to homes and businesses Australia-wide.	</div>
</div>
	<!-- #EndEditable -->



<!-- #BeginEditable "Content" -->
<div class="bodyCopy">
	
	<h2>Here are just some of the features and benefits of choosing Internode:</h2>
<ul>
<li>We really do love the Internet. And we love exceeding our customers expectations.</li>
<li>Our own high performance, high reliability, uncongested <a href="/about/our_network/">national and global network</a> dedicated to Internode customers, offering performance and reliability that are simply second to none. We believe there is no better and more consistently performing broadband service in Australia.</li>
<li>Friendly and caring staff offering free, expert support and sales advice, and based entirely 'in house' here at Internode. Mostly at our head office in Adelaide, but also in our other offices in Melbourne, Brisbane and Sydney.</li>
<li>Open and honest information (here are our <a href="/support/faq/">FAQs</a> and <a href="/about/performance/">live phone queue stats</a>) and dialogue with our customers about Internode, about our services, and about what drives us. <a href="/about/follow_us_online/">Follow us</a> on Twitter and Facebook, or chat with us on the Whirlpool Broadband Forums.</li>
<li>Nationally available <a href="/residential/">home</a> and <a href="/business/">business</a> services featuring our ever popular <a href="/residential/adsl_broadband/">Easy ADSL2+ broadband</a>; our home phone product <a href="/residential/phone_and_voip/nodeline_home_phone/">NodeLine</a>; and our great-value VoIP solution <a href="/residential/phone_and_voip/nodephone_voip/">NodePhone</a>.</li>
<li>An easy <a href="/coverage">online signup process</a> for broadband services, offered on a no-success, no-fee basis.</li>
<li>Customer access plans that are designed with a customer focus, including fixed cost 'shaped' plans, monthly quotas you can use anytime (without needing to wait for peak or offpeak periods), and the extra flexibility to buy additional <a href="/residential/product_features/data_blocks/">data blocks</a> on demand if your requirements change from month to month.</li>
<li>Free and user-configurable Spam Filtering, Virus blocking, and other useful <a href="/residential/product_features/email/">online mail services</a>.</li>
<li>One of the largest and most popular <a href="http://games.on.net/">Online Gaming Services </a>in Australia - unmetered for Internode customers.</li>
<li>Cool freebies like our <a href="/iphone/">iPhone and iPod touch applications</a>, and an ever growing number of free <a href="https://hotspot.internode.on.net/coverage/">WiFi Hotspots</a> around Australia.</li>
<li>A huge range of <a href="/residential/entertainment/broadband_radio/">high quality streaming 'radio' stations</a>, exclusive to Internode customers and <em>unmetered</em> - meaning you can listen all day without affecting your download quota!</li>
<li>A <a href="http://mirror.internode.on.net/">massive unmetered File Server</a> (with Terabytes of available downloads).</li>
<li>Simple and minimal contract terms, and the freedom to bring your own broadband hardware, or to <a href="/residential/hardware/">purchase your hardware from Internode</a>.</li>
<li>Ease of transfer to Internode from other providers - we participate in all industry fast transfer processes.</li>
<li>Up to four free additional mailboxes and personal web space with each broadband account.</li>
<li>We give a damn. :)</li>
</ul>
<h3>More to explore</h3>
<p>Learn even more about how we provide a high quality, stress-free Internet experience - by browsing through our recent <a href="/news">news</a> and <a href="/awards">awards</a>, our company and its history, our network and our management team - all located in the menu to the left.</p>
<p>And browse through our range of innovative <strong><a href="/residential/">Residential</a></strong> and <strong><a href="/business/">Business</a></strong> products, designed to deliver you the best possible value and performance in Internet, voice and data solutions</p>
<h3>Some thoughts from our founder</h3>
<p>"Internode is a First Tier Internet services provider. We use the best technology, harnessed by our excellent network design team, to deliver the best end-to-end network service we know how to build. We provide a consistently reliable service that we deeply care about, whether you're a business, corporation, government department or home user."</p>
<p style="text-align: right;"><em>- Simon Hackett, Internode Founder</em></p>	
</div>
